 * Source Tables:   shadow_OUTPUT0 - work.collateral      A5ZNM6KG.BV0004LA * 
 *                  shadow_OUTPUT0 -                      A5ZNM6KG.BV0004LB * 
 *                   work.collateral_giver                                  * 
 *                  shadow_OUTPUT0 - work.customer        A5ZNM6KG.BV0004LC * 
